Section: misc
Priority: optional
Description: A python script to display Raspberry Pi statistcis on a 128x32 Mini OLED.
 This script was created and adapted from here https://bit.ly/3rjHarP
 The script displays the following stats on the OLED:
 Line 1: IP Address and hostname (alternating every approx. 10 seconds)
 Line 2: CPU Load [%]
 Line 3: Mem usage: [%] of total Memory
 Line 4: Disk usage: used/total GB [%]

